{"tid":1888255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉遵義退任希慎獨立非執董 曾撰文支持成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2020-02-20T05:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T05:48:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18a1a68f4f511f1414ee2c32d4c4de32c03a03af","tid":1888255,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"希慎興業公布，劉遵義將會退任集團獨立非執行董事及提名委員會成員職務。<br />\n<br />\n希慎指，基於提名委員會對現有董事委員會成員架構作出檢討後，宣布由另一位獨立非執董卓百德接任提名委員會成員，股東周年大會完結後生效。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，劉遵義已確定與董事會並無任何意見分歧，就退任一事並無任何事項需要通知股東。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509689-20200220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509689-20200220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=973ae39d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509689-20200220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1c4cb05d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509689-20200220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>劉遵義<br />\n中大藍饒富暨藍凱麗經濟學講座教授<br />\n<br />\n香港正經歷一場前所未有的嚴重危機。更可悲的是，這本不該發生。但覆水難收，現在真的不是相互指責的時候。成立獨立調查委員會，對逃犯條例修訂案事件的前因後果進行全面調查，可能會有助於我們今後避免類似的危機，因此不妨一試。我們必須繼續前行，但它（獨立調查委員會）並不能給我們太多的指引。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-07/29/35623.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2019-07%2F29%2F35623.html&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=e056c234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2019-07/29/35623.html</a>"},{"pid":"ad145072c254c5354b9a597eed629a4a679c0ce4","tid":1888255,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"支共連膠樽都唔當係自已人啊!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}